            <thetext>Generating the testrunner for the framework does not work. After evaluating 
whats the problem i found out that the generator generates a wrong uri into the 
tests-source.html file. The reference to the testrunner.TestLoader class is 
wrong and that causes the the loader not to load all classes listed after that 
wrong reference. 
The right uri would be 
&quot;../../../component/testrunner/source/class/testrunner/TestLoader.js&quot; but the 
generator generates that uri &quot;../../source/class/testrunner/TestLoader.js&quot;.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
